title: The Edinburgh tales.
author: Johnstone, C. I.
snippet: That charmingly situated and most desirable Marine Villa," &c. &c. there followed in the Bankrupt list lo ! and behold ! it was no mistake : " Meeting of the creditors of Duncan Smith, merchant, to be held in the Tontine, &c. &c. for the purpose of appointing  an interim factor."
